Definition.WordDefinition:
Starlight \Star"light`\ (-l[imac]t`), n. The light given by the stars. [1913 Webster]
Nor walk by moon, Or glittering starlight, without thee is sweet. --Milton. [1913 Webster]

Dictionary.Name: The Collaborative International Dictionary of English v.0.44

Definition.WordDefinition:
Starlight \Star"light`\, a. Lighted by the stars, or by the stars only; as, a starlight night. [1913 Webster]
A starlight evening and a morning fair. --Dryden. [1913 Webster]
starlight n : the light of the stars
